class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#000000\"><!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":64} -->\n<div style=\"height:64px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\".9\"}},\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-small-font-size\" style=\"line-height:.9\"><strong>문의하기</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":59,\"lineHeight\":\"1.15\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\" id=\"schedule-a-visit\" style=\"font-size:59px;line-height:1.15\"><strong>방문 예약</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\",\"orientation\":\"horizontal\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button {\"width\":50,\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#000000\",\"text\":\"#ffffff\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"50px\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-50\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-text-color has-background\" style=\"border-radius:50px;background-color:#000000;color:#ffffff\">연락처</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":64} -->\n<div style=\"height:64px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:2:\"id\";i:333860;s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:26:\"Three column pricing table\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:3785:\"\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-9 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-bottom:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-1a0bc8f67789925faa0962e3a30e6ba9 is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffe97d;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"single\" style=\"font-size:40px\"><strong>싱글</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.5\"><strong>지역사회에 도움을 주세요.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-css-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#000000;color:#000000\" />\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-normal-font-size\">\n<li>성인 한 명의 일반 입장료 및 회원 할인 혜택</li>\n\n\n\n<li>특별 전시회 무료 입장권 한 장</li>\n\n\n\n<li>1년에 두 번 일회용 게스트 패스</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons alignfull is-horizontal is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-3 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-100\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-white-color has-text-color has-background no-border-radius wp-element-button\" style=\"background-color:#000000\">$110 / 연</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-5c1fa33762204a23c4dbb75569ab4aad is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#d1d1e1;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"family\" style=\"font-size:40px\"><strong>가족</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.5\"><strong>특별전을 지원해보세요.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity is-style-wide\" />\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-normal-font-size\">\n<li>성인 2명 입장 시 일반 입장료 및 회원 할인 제공</li>\n\n\n\n<li>특별전 한 회당 4장의 무료 입장권</li>\n\n\n\n<li>연간 4회 일회용 게스트 패스권</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons alignfull is-horizontal is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-5 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-100 is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-white-color has-text-color has-background no-border-radius wp-element-button\" style=\"background-color:#000000\">$200 / 년</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-9bf0ae972a06f7c981e766b290d848de is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#c0ebf1;padding-top:2em;padding-right:2em;padding-bottom:2em;padding-left:2em\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"patron\" style=\"font-size:40px\"><strong>후원자</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\"><strong>다음 한 단계를 위해 지원하세요.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity is-style-wide\" />\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-normal-font-size\">\n<li>성인 2명 입장 시 일반 입장료 및 회원 할인 제공</li>\n\n\n\n<li>각 특별전의 무료 입장권 5장</li>\n\n\n\n<li>연간 6회 일회용 게스트 패스</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons alignfull is-horizontal is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-7 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-100\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-white-color has-text-color has-background no-border-radius wp-element-button\" style=\"background-color:#000000\">$400 / 년</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:4:\"meta\";O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:13:\"wpop_keywords\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"wpop_description\";s:277:\"세 개의 동일한 너비의 열을 가격 표로 설정합니다. 왼쪽 열은 노란색 배경, 가운데 열은 밝은 보라색 배경, 오른쪽 열은 밝은 파란색 배경입니다. 각 열에는 제목, 하위 제목, 구분 기호, 목록, 버튼이 있습니다.\";s:19:\"wpop_viewport_width\";i:1200;s:16:\"wpop_block_types\";a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}s:11:\"wpop_locale\";s:5:\"ko_KR\";s:15:\"wpop_wp_version\";s:0:\"\";s:25:\"wpop_contains_block_types\";s:117:\"core/button,core/buttons,core/column,core/columns,core/heading,core/list,core/list-item,core/paragraph,core/separator\";}s:14:\"category_slugs\";a:2:{i:0;s:14:\"call-to-action\";i:1;s:8:\"featured\";}s:13:\"keyword_slugs\";a:1